commit.message:
This is an unpackaged folder for the hack hate speech extension

In order to run/test this extension go to chrome://extensions/

Check off the developer mode near the top right of the page. It will
ask you to choose a file to upload.

Upload this entire folder and an icon should appear near the address
bar.
